1-AM.png?resize=1024%2C343&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmamas/files/2019/12/Screen-Shot-2019-12-10-at-10.36.41-AM.png?w=1280 1280w, https://i1.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmamas/files/2019/12/Screen-Shot-2019-12-10-at-10.36.41-AM.png?w=1920 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></noscript></p>
<p>Sincerely,<br />
The Editors of Math Mamas<br />
Emille, Rachelle, and Amanda</p>
