<p><span style="font-weight: 400">[P] Pelletier, A. (2006) </span><span style="font-weight: 400">Family Medical Leave Act of 1993 &#8211; Why Does Parental Leave in the United States Fall so Far behind Europe? </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400">Gonzaga Law Review</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400"> 547.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">[R] Rehel, E. M. (2014). When dad stays home too: Paternity leave, gender, and parenting. </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400">Gender and Society, 28</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400">, 110–132. </span></p>
