<p><span style="font-weight: 400"> </span><span style="font-weight: 400">[RS] Rossin-Slater, M. Ruhm, C. J., and Waldfogel, J</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400">. </span></i><span style="font-weight: 400">(2011).</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400"> The Effects of California’s Paid Family Leave Program on Mothers’ Leave-taking and Subsequent Labor Market Outcomes.</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400">  NBER Working Paper 17715, National Bureau of Economic Research (</span><a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w17715.pdf"><span style="font-weight: 400">https://www.nber.org/papers/w17715.pdf</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">)</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">[Ru] Ruhm, C. (1998).  The Economic Consequences of Parental Leave Mandates: Lessons from Europe, </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400">The Quarterly Journal of Economics</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400">, Vol. 113, No. 1, pp. 285-317.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
